Detailed Description

cvmx_nqm_vf::_sq::_tdbl

NQM_VF(x)_SQ(y)_TDBL is the NVMe-standard submission queue y tail doorbell (SQyTDBL) for function x. Includes both admin and IO queues. NQM_VF_MODE[VF_MODE] selects the queues and functions that are actually present in the hardware. See NQM_VF_MODE_E.

This CSR should only be migrated when the corresponding SQ is idle. The corresponding NQM_VF()_SQ()_ENA[ENABLE] is an enable for the SQ. NQM_VF()_SQ()_ENA[ENABLE] describes SQ idle conditions.
